		<h1>Goals</h1>

		<p>The goals of the TenDRA project are:</p>

		<ol class="goals">
			<li>To continuously <em>produce correct code</em>,</li>

			<li>to <em>ensure code correctness</em> through various means,</li>

			<li>to continuously improve the performance of the compiler and
				resulting code, <em>unless it would jeopardise the points above</em>.</li>
		</ol>

		<p>See the <a href="#">Status page</a> for supported platforms and features.</p>

		<h1>Get Involved</h1>

		<p>Getting your feet wet is pretty easy; <a href="#">check out the
