			development suggestions <a href="#">on tickets</a>. We'll be
			happy to hear your thoughts; see the <a href="#">Contact</a>
			page for details.</p>

		<p>You can also follow <a href="#">RSS
			feeds</a> for most of the interesting things on this site.</p>
